sānandetyādi. sahānandena vartata iti sānandam. sānandaṃ ca tat sallakṣaṇamaṇḍitāṅgaṃ ca sambhujyamānaṃ dharmadeśanādvāreṇopajīvyamānam. kaiḥ? daśabhūmīśvaraiḥ, pariśiṣṭabhūmisthitānām agocaratvāt. daśabhūmiprāptair avalokiteśvaramañjuśrīprabhṛtibhir upabhujyamānam iti yāvat. etad uktaṃ bhavati—śuddhāvāsopari ghanavyūhasaṃjñake samyaksaṃbuddhabhuvane yathā bhagavān ānandarūpaḥ sambhogakāyātmā nirmāṇadvāreṇa sakalajagadarthasaṃpādakaḥ śrāvakapratyekabuddhanavabhūmīśvarair apy adṛśyaśarīro daśabhūmīśvarair eva paraṃ bodhisattvair dharmaśravaṇadvāreṇopabhujyamāna āsaṃsāraṃ cakāsti, tathaiva tat sādhyam iti tṛtīyam.